item.title: TIL: My actual height
item.author: cancheta.dev@gmail.com (Charles Ancheta)
item.description: Today I learned what my actual height was (at least at the time of writing). For a few years now I’ve always kind of just stuck with 170 cm because that’s what was in my driver’s license when I got it 5 years ago (I really need to pass the road test this year). I’m not even sure if that was right at the time.
